data.description: ASSUMABLE 3% FHA LOAN! $5000 TOWARD CLOSING COSTS! PRICED BELOW FHA APPRAISAL!! NEW ROOF 8/8 and a home that's ready for you to make it yours. Step into the charm of this 3-bedroom, 2-bath house with a bright and open layout that welcomes you in. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor, offers both comfort and seclusion. Glide into the galley kitchen that balances functionality and style, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and a seamless connection to the adjoining dining area. Upstairs, discover two cozy bedrooms and a shared bathroom - perfect for guests or crafting your own home office sanctuary. Sunlight bathes every corner of this home, enveloping it in a warm and inviting ambiance. A thoughtful design and sought-after amenities make this house the perfect space to call your own. But that's not all - the backyard is a true treasure. Envision memorable outdoor gatherings on the spacious covered patio. And there's more: an extended slab patio and a generously-sized storage building offer flexibility, letting you mold the backyard to your desires. Nestled in a convenient location with rapid access to I-35 and 1604, you're minutes away from shopping, parks, and schools. Act now to seize this opportunity. Verify room dimensions and schools to make this fantastic property your own!
